            <td class="px-4 py-3 text-stone-600 border border-stone-200">Strategy & Ops, BizOps, Central Operations</td>
            <td class="px-4 py-3 text-stone-600 border border-stone-200">战略分析、运营分析、增长运营、商业化运营</td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="border-b border-stone-100">
            <td class="px-4 py-3 font-medium text-stone-700 border border-stone-200">工作重心</td>
