            <td class="px-4 py-3 text-stone-600 border border-stone-200">执行导向更强，数据报表和业务支持占比更高</td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="border-b border-stone-100">
            <td class="px-4 py-3 font-medium text-stone-700 border border-stone-200">汇报层级</td>
